dog bite dog ( chinese : &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; ) is a 2006 hong kong action crime thriller film directed by &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; cheang and starring edison chen as a brutal cambodian assassin , desperately trying to evade the police , led by sam lee , after completing an assignment in hong kong . the film was released in hong kong cinemas on 17 august 2006 .